{"word":"Rehoboam","slug":"rehoboam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rehoboam</b> <a href=\"#/H7346\">H7346</a> <br/> Successor to Solomon as king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=43'>1Ki 11:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=31'>2Ch 9:31</a><br/> Refuses to reform abuses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=15'>1Ki 12:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=10&verse=15'>2Ch 10:15</a><br/> Ten tribes, under leadership of Jeroboam, successfully revolt from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=24'>1Ki 12:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=10&verse=19'>2Ch 10:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=4'>2Ch 11:4</a><br/> Builds fortified cities; is temporarily prosperous<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=23'>2Ch 11:23</a><br/> Invaded by king of Egypt and despoiled<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=28'>1Ki 14:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=12'>2Ch 12:12</a><br/> Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=31'>1Ki 14:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=16'>2Ch 12:16</a><br/> Genealogy and descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3'>1Ch 3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1'>Mat 1</a><br/> Called Roboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=7'>Mat 1:7</a>"}]}